metadata.name: Anti-control Doll kingdom
metadata.description:
AI Doll anti-control story... 
There are too many PUA in the world, moral kidnapping things, bad temper can control good temper, bullying such incidents are NG. I intend to draw a series on this theme: anti-control Dolls.
